Servings: 6 <!--more-->

Preparation Time: 10 minutes 

Cooking Time:

Cuisine: Thai 

#### INGREDIENTS 
* 1 tbsp Coconut Oil 
* 1 -4 oz can [Sour Yellow Curry Paste](https://amzn.to/2XUUbLX)
* 1 can Coconut Milk
* 1 medium Yellow Onion, roughly chopped
* 3-4 Carrots, cut into 1-inch battons 
* 5 Red or Yukon Potatoes, cut into 1-inch pieces
* 1 Zuchinni, cut into 1-inch pieces
* 1 lb Chicken Thighs, boneless and skinless, cut into bit-size pieces 
---
3 Garlic Cloves, minced
Ginger, minces 
Thai Basil 
1 tbsp Fish Sauce

