### ABOUT THE MEAL

#### What main ingredients do I need for this meal?

* Chicken 
* Vegetables: I used onions, potatoes, zucchinis, and carrots. 
* Sour [Sour Yellow Thai Curry Paste](https://amzn.to/2XUUbLX)

#### What equipment do I need to make this recipe?

* A [heavy-bottomed pan](https://amzn.to/3kQSCYw) 

#### Can I freeze Thai curry?
You sure can. First, allow the curry to cool completely, and then add it to a freezer-safe container or bag. When youâ€™re ready to eat, let it defrost in the frige overnight. To serve, warm it on the stove and prepare your sides.

